## Overview

dddstack is a collection of open source packages for beautiful, dynamic, and modern applications.

## Installation

```bash
npm install @dddstack/PACKAGE
```

## Usage

```jsx
import { dddstack } from "@dddstack/PACKAGE";

const DddStack = () => {
  return <div class={dddstack}>dddstack</div>;
};

export default Dddstack;
```
